
MachoKillers By Mellow Chips
----------------------------

Coding...   by Petri "Braindead" Häkkinen
Graphics... by Olli "OLA" Hänninen-Pelz and Tomas "Lich" Björnfot
Samples...  by various PD authors, Thank You



This game is written using Amos Professional V2.0 in 1 single day. 
It's Public Domain, so feel free to do whatever you want with it.
So keep it, it's all yours! 8-)




